flowchart 

    A(User completes the form) --> B(Event handler activation)
    B --> C[Prevent default form submission]
    C --> D{Create new note object}
    D --> E{Add note to the list}
    E --> F[Render the list of notes]
    F --> G{Send new note to the server}
    G --> H{Process data on the server}
    H --> I[Response with status code 201]
    I --> J{Update user interface}
    J --> K[End]
